5A39A25C.Line1.9118B: The swamp is always watching. It knows why you've come. It knows each and every bone that has sunk to the bottom of the black mud since time began.

6337820B.VoiceDir3.9118B: Referring to the Tree of Whispers

F42E1BDE.Line3.9118B: It sees all and more, and its wisdom grows with every fool who makes a pact with the Tree.
